        <h3>About the Event</h3>
        <p>This event is focused on beautifying our community by organizing clean-up drives in local parks, streets, and beaches.</p>
        
        <h3>Achievements</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Cleaned up 10 parks, 15 streets, and 3 beaches.</li>
            <li>Collected over 5 tons of trash.</li>
            <li>Engaged 300 volunteers in clean-up activities.</li>
            <li>Improved the aesthetic appeal of public spaces.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Pros</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Enhanced the cleanliness and beauty of the community.</li>
            <li>Increased community pride and ownership.</li>
            <li>Reduced pollution in public spaces.</li>
            <li>Fostered a sense of environmental responsibility.</li>
        </ul>
        
